{"tid":1952296,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抖音封禁廣東話片 「整改建议：请尽量使用普通话」","createTime":"2020-03-31T13:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T04:41:23.000Z","uid":175540,"like":2,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea9c179d69c1ad4b7c72c4b5e437c04563d93ce","tid":1952296,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"有廣州網友向港語學投訴，指近日喺大陸社交平台「抖音」上有主播進行廣東話直播期間，竟然俾抖音封禁；系統訊息更加列出「整改建议：请尽量使用普通话」。投訴信附上電話截圖，訊息指該主播「違反直播行為規範」。<br />\n<br />\n港語學呼籲市民切勿使用「抖音」&mdash;&mdash;一個表面上係娛樂軟件，實則由國家機器審核內容嘅洗腦平台。用抖音唔單止會影響思想，更加可能洩露個人資料，累己累人。<br />\n<br />\n2017年，中华人民共和国教育部頒布《国家通用语言文字普及攻坚工程实施方案》，揚言：「強國必先強語，強語助力強國。」又謂「扶貧首要扶智，扶智應先通語」，普通話唔普及將危及「民族團結和諧」，所以必須確保全國普通話普及率到 2020 年達到 80% 甚至更高云云。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驚到</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該得極權國家先咁驚"},{"pid":"51ca2f9963e291a0d980ef1877702772aae1e0cd","tid":1952296,"uid":1517,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"本身玩佢呢個app已經on9"},{"pid":"06090ef01099524b7de9e60171e3ffe73e0fba59","tid":1952296,"uid":342219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UBDqlu-36GkZZIJ3K0wuRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FUBDqlu-36GkZZIJ3K0wuRg&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIht9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=0d4a304c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UBDqlu-36GkZZIJ3K0wuRg</a>"},{"pid":"478722a4cd431f527081e7813c92ea1fb41610a1","tid":1952296,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"你個post得兩個回覆都俾lihkg fb admin 睇中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2912220065541374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%